article_title: Aetna May Expand Obamacare To More States For 2017

article_metadata.description: Aetna could join Centene, Anthem and its family of Blue Cross and Blue Shield plans in expanding to new markets on public exchanges under the Affordable Care Act for 2017.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
